230. Kth Smallest Element in BST
Medium
Related: 98. Validate Binary Tree

Intuition:
Since BST's representation is a sorted array, we simply traverse through the tree using inorder traversal.
Then return the k-1th element of the array

Approach:
1) use DFS(L-P-R) to fill the array
2) return k-1 st element

Complexity:
Time -> O(n) -> run through the tree once
Space -> O(n) -> allocate space for n values in array